e=66E42749"}, "display_name": "Winery Tour in Georgia", "keywords": ["Wine", "Travel", "WineryTour", "Food", "History"], "long_description": "Georgian winemaking method is a part of UNESCO Intangible Heritage. It is the longest uninterrupted tradition of creating wine in the world. Georgia is also one of the oldest winegrowing countries - the pips of the grapes that have been found at Shulaveri Gora historical site are witnessing the fact that the locals were cultivating vines here around 8000 years ago.\nHow does a winery visit look like, once you're in Georgia? Of course, it's a bit of history, a bit of technology, and of course, some excellent food, drinks, songs, and toasts. Take a tour in Giuaani Winery in Manavi (Kakheti), discover more about the Georgian wine, and attend the friendly Georgian supra with the international visitors afterward!\nOf course, this is a demo version that gives you an idea about a half a day winery tour - it takes only one hour to get there from Tbilisi. But a deeper immersion will take you a bit longer. More wineries, more tastings, more exciting landscapes... Georgia is very diverse!", "short_description": "Visit Giuaani Winery in Kakheti with Trails and Wines, and learn more about the Georgian wine and winemaking peculiarities"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "http://privacy.vrexbox.com/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "VRex Immersive Inc.", "support_website_url": "http://vr-ex.com/", "website_url": "http://vr-ex.com/", "category": "APPS", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_SOME", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["EXPERIENCE_360_NON_GAME", "TRAVEL", "EXPLORATION"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": null, "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_i